remarks.format: ## Remarks 将 XAML 命名空间前缀映射到的完整 XAML 命名空间 URI。 maps XAML namespace prefixes to the complete XAML namespace URI. 有关 XAML 中的应用程序的使用情况和在常规的 XAML 命名空间，URI 通常不是架构样式 URI，其中包含`http://`。For XAML usage in applications and XAML namespaces in general, the URI is often not a schema-style URI that includes `http://`. 它改为是用户定义的映射到 CLR 命名空间和程序集。It is instead a user-defined mapping to a CLR namespace and assembly. 程序集包含后备类型所引用。That assembly contains the backing types being referred to. 有关详细信息，请参阅[XAML 命名空间和 WPF XAML Namespace 映射](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/xaml-namespaces-and-namespace-mapping-for-wpf-xaml.md)。For details, see [XAML Namespaces and Namespace Mapping for WPF XAML](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/xaml-namespaces-and-namespace-mapping-for-wpf-xaml.md). 添加 XAML 命名空间的作用域的概念。The adds the concept of scope for a XAML namespace. 默认值可能包含前缀键和 XML 命名空间 URI 值。A default might contain prefix keys and XML namespace URI values. 中的作用域概念与 XML 概念，可能会重新定义前缀。The scope concept in parallels the XML concept that a prefix might be redefined. 如果是这样，重新定义仅适用该级别或下面 （上一个定义应用在 DOM 中的高级别） 的 xml DOM 视图中。If so, the redefinition only applies at that level or below in a DOM view of the XML (the previous definition applies at higher level in the DOM). 作用域概念中抽象主要出API，例如，您可以调用 Api 如而无需担心作用域。The scope concept is mostly abstracted away in the API, such that you can call APIs such as without being concerned about scope. 但是，确实公开并，以便自定义更改作用域的实现可以同步的作用域。However, does expose and so that a custom implementation that changes scope can synchronize with the scope for the .
